#' @param timeUnit (_FieldOrDatumDefWithCondition<StringFieldDef,string>_) Time unit (e.g., `year`, `yearmonth`, `month`, `hours`) for a temporal field. or [a temporal field that gets casted as ordinal](https://vega.github.io/vega-lite/docs/type.html#cast).
#' 
#' __Default value:__ `undefined` (None)
#' 
