#' @param gradientLength (_Legend_)  
#' @param gradientOpacity (_Legend_)  
#' @param gradientStrokeColor (_Legend_)  
#' @param gradientStrokeWidth (_Legend_)  
#' @param gradientThickness (_Legend_)  
#' @param gridAlign (_Legend_)  
